{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5e0c4a14ec","title":"大字报——这样搞对吗？","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑3》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月25日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ee3a0a2b25","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"222c241b8a","name":"成都工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"01e7bede45","type":"title","text":"大字报——这样搞对吗？","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"2115d31511","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"e4db876bc8","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反的目的在于消除反革命，这完全是对的。可是我们看一下，我们学院党委领导下的肃反到底如何？我们不说反革命有多少，应如何处理，单说在肃反中对一般教职工和同学的态度问题，他们并非反革命，然而被剥夺了通讯和行动自由，试问肃反的对象如何？党委的评论是“为了防止万一这样好一点”，难道这能掩饰违反宪法的事实吗？事实上这样的防止万一，不知党委考虑过没有能否达到其目的，还值得深思，有歌曰：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"3918b46f92","type":"paragraph","text":"禁事于高阁今尤能取其生效，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"001c0879fd","type":"paragraph","text":"囚非事于绣闱公安有补益，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"cccc656106","type":"paragraph","text":"日守闺阁今朝日盼解，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"ca68824b4f","type":"paragraph","text":"凤望凰今有大翅而难任其并飞，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"c91b325f91","type":"paragraph","text":"独望楼台今凄望孤灯，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"2a96f98de0","type":"paragraph","text":"千里看故今日夜盼乡土。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"37f6d39d7b","type":"paragraph","text":"善哉！党委，谢尔独特大命于施，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"3c1d3fa8c3","type":"paragraph","text":"恶哉！是人已当非子，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"c9b1469ca4","type":"paragraph","text":"呜乎！人权何在？公理何在？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"1c65ffbae5","type":"paragraph","text":"另一反宪法事实，我们不能不看到在肃反私拆“坏人”信件，说是什么把问题搞清楚，我的天哪上帝才知道。有打油为证！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"9e4ca5f144","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法上有通讯自由，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"26bce84c54","type":"paragraph","text":"但却有私将书信抽，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"},{"id":"2711bd328b","type":"paragraph","text":"拆信时好似虎寻食………","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec"}],"page":{"id":"8abbb6a0e6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5e0c4a14ec","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}